{
  "texts": [
    "Another baseline is promptscoring.",
    "With this approach, for a particular attribute, the LLMs is asked to assess the response quality between 1-10.",
    "Simple prompts are used with the general templates shown in Figure 3.",
    "Prompt-scoring is run for all open-source LLMs considered (FlanT5 and Llama2), and is used as the main baseline to compare comparative assessment against.",
    "During generation, the maximum generation length is set to 5 and the temperature is set to 1.0."
  ]
}